{"tid":2504395,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿JER 好撚黃......","createTime":"2021-04-26T00:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T04:34:40.000Z","uid":70964,"like":22,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"87bd5d1a2dbc59514ba3e9835bce2eea2762a242","tid":2504395,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T00:28:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210425/UIK5NGC7JRA3TC22Y2KULG762E/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1t91bejEjikYRu1qAyImJCQv4ZMNta7KxfrGVHhswkgVLcQZySwSCTRVA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210425%2FUIK5NGC7JRA3TC22Y2KULG762E%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1t91bejEjikYRu1qAyImJCQv4ZMNta7KxfrGVHhswkgVLcQZySwSCTRVA&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepF%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=7a181a77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210425%2FUIK5NGC7JRA3TC22Y2KULG762E%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1t91bejEjikYRu1qAyImJCQv4ZMNta7KxfrGVHhswkgVLcQZySwSCTRVA&h=960bcc0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210425/UIK5NGC7JRA3TC22Y2KULG762E/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1t91bejEjikYRu1qAyImJCQv4ZMNta7KxfrGVHhswkgVLcQZySwSCTRVA</a>"},{"pid":"3f9b96e6e0c24bff42e4738a74146a7900a8ea70","tid":2504395,"uid":70964,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T00:29:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><strong><span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"green\">「相信何桂藍聽完我嘅歌都釋懷」</span></span></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n本住自己會是黑暗中的一點光去唱，令阿Jer唱出心情：「我初頭聽自己嘅聲音又唔覺得有咁大嘅力量嘅，我當然每一首歌都好投入去唱，希望將嗰個心情唱畀大家聽，《物語》系列好dark，但都要畀能量自己、相信自己就係嗰點光，我都好相信我自己嘅歌，何桂藍聽完之後，可能會有好多唔開心，聽完之後都釋懷、釋放，正正就係我上年做歌嗰個目的，希望影響到更加多人，我嚟緊會200%擺喺歌曲度，可以令大家喺唔開心嘅環境下，都有力量繼續行落去。」<br />\n<br />\n在訪問之前，阿Jer已是今年度樂壇新人獎的大贏家，再到上星期日，他在ViuTV首屆Chill Club推介榜年度推介中，以近半票數拿下年度新人獎。得到獎項肯定，他謙虛說：「其實我開心嘅，最幫到我嘅一樣嘢就係喺舞台上嘅自信，對自己作品嘅信心都增強，呢樣嘢對我幫助好大。其實以前夾band嘅時候喺舞台上都有信心，因為之前參加《造星》由頭到尾都係輸，人生好似扣唔上贏呢個主題，所以自己喺舞台上嘅信心真係弱啲。」今年目標會是男歌手獎嗎？他說：「我又冇諗過，希望可以裝備自己多啲先，我寧願成為一個大家認同嘅歌手先至攞男歌手，多過未夠班就去攞，我寧願等耐啲，我而家都係新人階段啫，男歌手獎對我嚟講係好遙遠嘅事，成績只係bonus，只要做到作品係影響到樂迷，可以令大家留意廣東歌，咁先係做一個音樂人最想做嘅嘢，多過攞一個獎。」"},{"pid":"75f5fe3dead1a16c14a2eb4810e7f6b43042c4e4","tid":2504395,"uid":172190,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T00:33:21.000Z","msg":"達哥仲黃"},{"pid":"91351e1fac50519e81311b0b2eb2436bc92060e9","tid":2504395,"uid":70964,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T00:33:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">推比立場姐姐知 </span>"},{"pid":"2cc4c78707e61cd2477f89c1195fb6ec5820f2e5","tid":2504395,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T01:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a5e912cc48b4c61d6e87802458a0b85c6cb1a5","tid":2504395,"uid":27287,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T01:21:05.000Z","msg":"咪講啦<br />\n一陣黃衛兵又搵野屌 屌到一文不值"},{"pid":"b0bcac58b2b03d3b6256d68d48d49913ef417c4a","tid":2504395,"uid":3206,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:06:00.000Z","msg":"夠了     低調 plz"},{"pid":"a1a2fc4e45cbd11623fa3496b1144572e2569988","tid":2504395,"uid":3206,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T03:06:30.000Z","msg":"琴日已經有2 3個post<br />\n<br />\n推下佢d歌好過"},{"pid":"c486b4e500761dcf1edb6b1038a82cde6fabe3d1","tid":2504395,"uid":333263,"like":3,"dislike